skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: nutrition label
des: Nutrition Label lets you ask for common nutritional information on almost any food you can think of. Values are based on averages across different types of the requested food and its serving size.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
